<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="satisfy-vt">satisfy <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sætɪsfaɪ/    美 /'sætɪsfaɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 满足；(使) 满意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>satisfy sb’s needs / curiosity</strong> 
满足某人的需要/好奇心</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nick is looking for another job because he feels that nothing he does satisfies his boss. 
尼克正在找新工作，因为他感到老板对他做的工作都不满意。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>satisfying /'sætɪsfaɪɪŋ/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a satisfying meal 
可口的饭菜</p></div></div>